snippet.title: Batman: Arkham Underworld - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the city’s next criminal mastermind as you fight your way to the top in Batman: Arkham Underworld. This exciting new game in the Arkham franchise is now available for iPad and iPhone, and coming soon to Android!

Download now from iTunes: https://itunes.apple.com/ph/app/batman-arkham-underworld/id960120322?mt=8

For all the latest news on Batman: Arkham Underworld: http://www.dccomics.com/games/batman-arkham-underworld
#DC #DCComics #DCUniverse
